            <h3>Book Bank</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row contentfont">
        <div class="col-md-12 headerblack">
            <p class="contentP">
               Institute provides Department wise Book Bank facility to help the needy meritorious students. The Book Bank has a separate collection of books other than the library books. Book Bank is providing 4-6 books (as per availablity) to the student for the complete semester in the beginning of each academic session, apart from the normal facility of lending 2 books from Central Library.
            </p>
        </div>
        <br />
         <h5 class="h5">Rules For Book Bank Members</h5>
            <br />
         <ul class="contentP ul_li_p">
                <li>A student may get a maximum of six books from the Book Bank at a time.</li>
                <li>Books will be issued at beginning of each semester as per the schedule notified for the purpose.</li>
                <li>Books will be issued for whole semester. Student will be required to deposit the books after the completion of the exam as per the schedule notified.</li>
                <li>A fine will be levied if book will not be returned as per the schedule.</li>
                <li>Students will be responsible for any damage caused for the books. Students are advised to verify the physical condition of the books at time of its lending.</li>
                <li>If a book is lost the student will be required to pay the current market price of the book.</li>
                <li>Books will be issued on first come first served basis.</li>
            </ul><br />
    </div><br />
